# Dev Notes/Reminders

## Building EXE - Pyinstaller

```
C:\temp>pip install python-docx python-pptx pyinstaller
C:\temp>copy z:\dev\pptxindex\pptxindex.py .
C:\temp>pyinstaller --onefile --upx-exclude "vcruntime140.dll" --hidden-import docx --hidden-import pptx pptxindex.py
```

## Building an EXE - Nuitka

Use gcc.exe

```
nuitka --onefile --no-deployment-flag=self-execution pptxindex.py
```
